r-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg)"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style=" width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p></p><p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DByhvycImip/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">Brixtonbuzz (@brixtonbuzz) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p> Dogstar 最初名为 The Atlantic，它因曾被称为“布里克斯顿最引人注目的黑人酒吧”而闻名，并且是 1981 年布里克斯顿骚乱的中心。该场馆于 1994 年关闭，同年由 Antic London 重新开放并更名。</p><p>据<a href="https://mixmag.net/read/brixton-venue-the-dogstar-closure-squatters-london-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Mixmag</em></a>报道，Dogstar 也被称为英国最早的 DJ 酒吧之一，其鼓与贝斯之夜的表演嘉宾包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-streets">The Streets</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-skinner">Mike Skinner</a>以及 Fabio 和 Grooverider 等。</p><p>今年早些时候，音乐场馆信托基金 (Music Venue Trust) 发现，在“最具挑战性的一年”的主要调查结果中，去年有 125 个英国场馆放弃了现场音乐表演，其中超过一半已经完全关闭， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-music-venue-moles-in-bath-closes-after-45-years-today-is-a-very-sad-day-3553756">其中包括巴斯传奇的 Moles 场馆</a>。</p><p>其他历史悠久的场馆也面临关闭的风险——索尔福德小伙子俱乐部<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-salford-lads-club-the-site-of-the-most-famous-the-smiths-photo-faces-closure-3802716">由于成本上升和拨款资金减少而面临关闭的威胁</a>。为了保持开放，它必须在 11 月中旬之前筹集 25 万英镑。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/graham-nash-donates-10000-to-save-historic-salford-lads-club-3803347">格雷厄姆·纳什 (Graham Nash)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-donates-50000-to-help-save-salford-lads-club-the-location-of-the-iconic-the-smiths-photo-3808463">莫里西 (Morrissey</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-guitar-sale-and-oasis-exhibition-launched-to-help-save-salford-lads-club-3812433">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)</a>都在其中提供了帮助。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-venue-dogstar-taken-over-by-squatters-just-days-after-permanently-closing-3812438">布里克斯顿后的场地 Dogstar 在永久关闭几天后就被擅自占地者接管，该场地</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
