4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/happy_mondays_mtv_emas_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/happy_mondays_mtv_emas_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/happy_mondays_mtv_emas_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/happy_mondays_mtv_emas_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/happy_mondays_mtv_emas_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">Happy Mondays</a>与<em>NME</em>谈论了被废弃的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/SHAUN-RYDER">肖恩·莱德</a>传记片，并计划在 2025 年通过音乐“回归”。请观看下面的采访。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-happy-mondays-shaun-ryder-bez-mtv-emas-3811508">在颁奖典礼期间与瑞塔·奥拉 (Rita Ora) 一起“歇斯底里”地出现在网上疯传</a>之前，来自独立音乐偶像的莱德 (Ryder) 和贝兹 (Bez) 在周日（11 月 10 日）于 MTV EMA 的红地毯上赶上了<em>NME——</em>在 Co-Op Live 竞技场举行。乐队的故乡曼彻斯特。</p><p>当被问及 2024 年的星期一过得怎么样时，莱德回答道：“安静，因为我们在 2024 年遇到了一些麻烦。我们出去做了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-grape">《黑葡萄》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shaun-ryder-and-zak-starkey-on-mantra-of-the-cosmos-do-you-know-what-a-supergroup-means-four-guys-having-a-wank-3480446">《宇宙咒语》</a> ，所以 2025 年我们会回来的。” ”。</p><p>贝兹补充道：“我们让乐队再次重聚……再次！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DCUivlnTb-N/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; jus